<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> building <rs type="objectType">block</rs> without moulding (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.948</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.27</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.36</measure>), broken below and at the right end; surface damaged at lower left corner.</p>
